-- Force India Formula One Team Rehires Former Driver Adrian Sutil
-- B y   A l e x   D u f f
-- 2013-02-28T13:06:11Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-02-28/force-india-formula-one-team-rehires-former-driver-adrian-sutil.html
The Force India Formula One team
said it rehired Adrian Sutil, a racing driver it fired after the
end of the 2011 season.  The 30-year-old German will replace  Nico Hulkenberg , who
has moved to the Sauber team. The F1 championship opens on March
17 in Melbourne.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Alex Duff at 
 aduff4@bloomberg.net  